0.3.name: wordpress/targeter-app-plugin
0.3.description: Targeter App is Behavioral Targeting framework. You can take custom action based on the triggers selected. Triggers can be country of origin of visitor, time spent on page, engagement with the site, liking page on Facebook, tweeting your link, etc.
